<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Petition signaute</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div id="wrapper">
        <div class="join">Join Us!</div>
        <div class="lock"></div>
        <div class="clr"></div>
        <div class="login-options">
            <p>
                Ever wonder Why does Europe lacks grocery stores that are open 24 hours?
                the main reason is: some countires decided to protect employees rights by
                imposing legal restrictions on shop opening hours.
                Let's make a change without hurting employees rights!.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="clr"><hr /></div>
        <div class="mail-text">Please sign here, to have grocery stores opened around the clock!</div>
        <div class="forms">
            <form action="/petition" method="POST" name="petition">   
            <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{csrfToken}}" />
                <input type="hidden" name ="signature" id="siginput">       
                <canvas id="canvas" width="475" height="100" style="border: 1px solid black;">
                </canvas>
                <br />
                <input type="submit" value="submit" id="submit">
            </form>
        </div>

    </div>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.1.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="script.js"></script>

</body>

</html>
